title: Registration

contents: WiDS Claremont is an independent event organized by Manisha Goel, Jo Hardin, and Michelle Zemel to coincide with the annual Global Women in Data Science (WiDS) Conference held at Stanford University and an estimated 150+ locations worldwide. All genders are invited to attend WiDS regional events, which features outstanding women doing outstanding work.
